name: Fill The Page
description:
FILL THE PAGE

Control cube and collect points

How to play

Controls - Keyboard

Move - WASD

When above spot with a letter, press letter on your keyboard to get a point

If you hit border your current line will be filled but you will continue in next one

Try to get as many points as you can before you complete the page

Game was made in 4 days for Brackeys Game Jam 2023.1
